Load json file as spark data frame then get the latest record for the recipe.
Use contains command to filter the ingredient
Convert PT___ formatted time into minute for easy use
Get total cooking time in minute and use it to get difficulty level

Assumptions:
1) Recipe name is not changing
2) Recipe name is unique

Running the script:
Have to provide 4 arguments. Last one is optional
1) input_path: full qualified path for input json file
2) output_path_1: path for save filtered data as a csv
3) output_path_2: path for save average cooking time as a csv
4) filter_ingredient: (Optional) default: Beef  '